FBIS4-60642 "drnes103_j_94011" FBIS-NES-94-103 Daily Report 26 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Socialist Party Members Cable Support to Salih Socialist Party Members Cable Support to Salih JN2605174594 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 26 May 94 JN2605174594 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Brother Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, Presidential Council chairman, has received the following cable: We stress our support to Constitutional legitimacy and strongly condemn the declaration of secession. We once again underline our adherence to unity and readiness to defend it. [Signed] Your brothers, Dr. Muhammad 'Awad al-Sa'di, member of the Consultative Council [word indistinct] the Socialist Party Central Committee; Husayn [remainder of name indistinct], member of the House of Representatives and deputy for the (?129)th Constituency
